    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……あの魔物と一緒にいた仮面のヤツ、
誰だったんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That masked guy that was with the monsters back then... who the hell was he?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;、おまえ知ってるか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt;, do you know anything?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu~?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>知らないみたいだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It doesn't look like it knows anything...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>顔を隠さなきゃなんもできないって、
どうせ、ろくでもないヤツだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He didn't want people to look at his face... what a pathetic creep!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45616</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;？　どうしたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;, what's wrong?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、あ、ううん、あの人
なんかなつかしい匂いがした……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Err, ah, well, that person had a familiar feeling around him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>気のせい、かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Could it be my imagination?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、それならオレもしたぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now that you mention it, I think I kind of felt like that... I guess.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46112</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>香ばしい匂い。
あいつたぶんメシ食った後だぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's smell sure did feel familiar! It smelled like meat, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そういうんじゃなくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not what I was talking about...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか腹へったよ、
エト、食うもんないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh man am I hungry! Eto don't you wanna eat too?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きみねぇ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>………………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_006_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu~?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
